            "verse": 1,
            "text": "By the snorting, panting horses"
        },
        {
            "chapter": 100,
            "verse": 2,
            "text": "striking sparks of fire with their hooves"
        },
        {
            "chapter": 100,
            "verse": 3,
            "text": "as they gallop to make raids at dawn"
        },
        {
            "chapter": 100,
            "verse": 4,
            "text": "and raising clouds of dust"
        },
        {
            "chapter": 100,
            "verse": 5,
            "text": "forcing their way into the midst of the enemy"
        },
        {
            "chapter": 100,
            "verse": 6,
            "text": "surely, man is ungrateful to his Lord"
        },
        {
            "chapter": 100,
            "verse": 7,
            "text": "He himself bears witness to that"
        },
        {
            "chapter": 100,
            "verse": 8,
            "text": "Surely, he is ardent in his love of wealth"
        },
        {
            "chapter": 100,
            "verse": 9,
            "text": "Is he not aware of the time when the contents of the graves will be brought out"
        },
        {
            "chapter": 100,
            "verse": 10,
            "text": "And the hearts' contents shall be brought into the open"
        },
        {
            "chapter": 100,
            "verse": 11,
            "text": "Surely, on that Day, they will know that their Lord had full knowledge of them all"
